overview: Jasmine Vega: Did you see my grades dad? I worked sooo hard and I hope you're proud of me. I didn't go on any dates with any boys so I could stay home and study. Don't you think I deserve an award?  Victoria Voxxx: Do not treat me like a baby! I've seen the way you've been looking at me. You know, the way you try to sneak a peak at my ass when I'm bending over. Oh yeah, I've noticed that.  Danni Rivers: I like listening to the sound of my parents fucking. It actually turns me on. Late at night when they think I'm asleep, I can hear them through the wall going at each other.  Riley Star: My therapist appointment was ok, dad. All she really said was that I needed to get closer to my family. Maybe I can start with you?
title: My Daddy's Point of View 6
